
combat - simple OOP examples in C++, Perl and Python
------
combat.c - simple C program that generates the same ( more or less ) output. 
--------

combat.rb - simple ruby OOP program that does the same thing.
---------

perl driver code:
-----------------
combat.pl - driver that calls perl scripts to do aircraft or tank combat. Run this. 

perl modules and main code:
---------------------------
Weapon.pm - weapon class
aircraft_combat.pl - aircraft_combat perl script
tank_combat.pl - aircraft_combat perl script

python code:
------------
weapon_class.py - abstract weapon class for tanks and aircraft

python main code:
-----------------
do_combat_tank.py - do tank combat
do_combat_aircraft.py - do aircraft combat

Java code:
----------
Weapon.java      - weapon 
WeaponTest.java  - test the weapon 
TankCombat.java  - do tank combat 

C++ code:
---------
weapon.h         - weapon class
weapon.cpp       - weapon ( tanks, planes )
tank_combat.cpp  - tank combat
plane_combat.cpp - plane combat

